---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';

const updated = '2026-05-24';
---

<Layout title="Terms of Use — Sthira" description="Terms governing your use of the Sthira marketing site and waitlist.">
  <article class="mx-auto max-w-2xl px-6 py-20">
    <p class="text-sm font-medium uppercase tracking-wider text-slate-500">Legal</p>
    <h1 class="mt-3 text-4xl font-semibold tracking-tight">Terms of Use</h1>
    <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-slate-500">Last updated: {updated}</p>

    <div class="prose prose-slate mt-10 max-w-none prose-headings:font-semibold prose-headings:tracking-tight prose-h2:mt-10 prose-h2:text-2xl">
      <p>
        These terms govern your use of the Sthira marketing site at{' '}
        <strong>sthira.sosservices.online</strong>. Use of the Sthira app, when it opens,
        will be governed by a separate set of in-app terms reviewed against SEBI's IA
        regulations.
      </p>

      <h2>No investment advice on this site</h2>
      <p>
        Nothing on this site constitutes investment advice, a recommendation, or an offer
        to buy or sell securities. The waitlist form is purely a contact mechanism.
      </p>

      <h2>Closed pilot status</h2>
      <p>
        Sthira is in closed pilot pending SEBI Investment Advisor onboarding. Joining the
        waitlist does not guarantee access to the platform.
      </p>

      <h2>No warranties</h2>
      <p>
        This site is provided as-is. We make no warranties about uptime, accuracy of
        descriptions of unreleased features, or fitness for any particular purpose.
      </p>

      <h2>Limitation of liability</h2>
      <p>
        To the maximum extent permitted by law, SOS Services is not liable for indirect,
        incidental, or consequential damages arising from your use of this site.
      </p>

      <h2>Governing law</h2>
      <p>
        These terms are governed by the laws of India, with courts in Bangalore having
        exclusive jurisdiction.
      </p>

      <p class="text-sm text-slate-500">
        Questions? <a href="/contact">Contact us</a>.
      </p>
    </div>
  </article>
</Layout>
